  "chunks": [
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0001",
      "text": "Welcome to Dice Pyramid, a solo game of exploration and skill!",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        246.7,
        367.81,
        288.5
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0002",
      "text": "Journey deep into the heart of an ancient Egyptian pyramid, where each room does present a new challenge that will test your luck and strategy.",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        301.3,
        435.31,
        366.9
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0003",
      "text": "Roll the dice and match the challenges you face, from Unstable Stairways to Hall of Hieroglyphics, get powerful relics as you complete rooms and climb your way to the top of the pyramid and the ultimate prize: the Treasure Chamber containing the final riddle.",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        379.7,
        452.14,
        516.7
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0004",
      "text": "Are you ready to accept the challenge and conquer the pyramid?",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        529.5,
        440.38,
        571.3
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0005",
      "text": "Game Contents",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        30.6,
        185.5,
        52.6
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0006",
      "text": "• 15 Pyramid Cards",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        46.2,
        61.5,
        208.18,
        79.5
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0007",
      "text": "• Rulebook",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        46.2,
        123.2,
        140.23,
        141.2
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0008",
      "text": "Structure of a Pyramid Card",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        164.7,
        325.64,
        186.7
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0009",
      "text": "Each card is split into two parts: a room and a relic. Only one part -the one on top- is active at a time.",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        195.6,
        440.11,
        237.4
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0010",
      "text": "The cards are placed in the pyramid as rooms. When you complete a room, you place it on your side and rotate the card, so the relic side is on top.",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        250.2,
        451.2,
        315.8
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0011",
      "text": "Room side A room has 3 sections: name, challenge and description.",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        337.0,
        387.26,
        405.6
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0012",
      "text": "The challenge is what you need to do to complete the room. It is displayed using images (see “Reading the cards” for details). The description is a readable version of the challenge",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        32.0,
        452.21,
        121.4
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0013",
      "text": "Relic side A relic also has 3 sections: name, ability and description.",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        142.6,
        386.2,
        211.3
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0014",
      "text": "The ability is the effect that this relic provides. It is displayed using images (see “Reading the cards” for details). The description is a readable version of the ability",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        423.4,
        449.27,
        512.8
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0015",
      "text": "Game Setup",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        42.6,
        152.06,
        64.6
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0016",
      "text": "Take out the Treasure Chamber and Entrance rooms. Shuffle the remaining cards.",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        73.5,
        411.39,
        115.3
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0017",
      "text": "Place the Treasure Chamber on the table, face down. Build 2 rows under it with 2 and 3 cards respectively in the shape of a pyramid like this:",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        128.1,
        414.31,
        193.7
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0018",
      "text": "The rooms on the last row are the Initial Rooms that are available at the beginning of the game. To build this row, take 3 cards and shuffle them with the Entrance. Place them face up.",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        446.3,
        446.11,
        535.7
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0019",
      "text": "For optional rules and alternative setups, check the section “Optional Rules”.",
      "page": 4,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        548.5,
        440.2,
        590.3
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0020",
      "text": "How to play",
      "page": 5,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        42.6,
        151.82,
        64.6
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0021",
      "text": "You play turns until you obtain the Golden Ankh (complete the Treasure Chamber) or fail to complete a room with no relics left.",
      "page": 5,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        73.5,
        453.23,
        139.1
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0022",
      "text": "Turn Structure Roll all 5 dice.",
      "page": 5,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        160.3,
        156.22,
        205.2
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0023",
      "text": "Twice per turn, you can re-roll any number of dice.",
      "page": 5,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        218.0,
        428.21,
        236.0
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0024",
      "text": "You can use the ability of any relic you own anytime. A relic is discarded when used.",
      "page": 5,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        248.8,
        449.54,
        290.6
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0025",
      "text": "If your dice match the challenge of a room, you can take the pyramid card to your side and rotate it so the relic part is up. You can’t have more than 5 relics. If you obtain more, choose and discard down to 5.",
      "page": 5,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        303.4,
        453.16,
        392.8
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0026",
      "text": "If your dice match several challenges, you chose which one to complete.",
      "page": 5,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        405.6,
        421.25,
        447.4
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0027",
      "text": "When you take a pyramid card, if it was the last card covering a room, that room is now open. Flip it face up. Next turn you can also attempt its challenge.",
      "page": 5,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        460.2,
        450.12,
        525.8
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0028",
      "text": "If at the end of the turn your dice do not match any challenge, discard a relic to start a new turn. If you don’t have any relics to discard, you lose.",
      "page": 6,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        271.8,
        435.13,
        337.4
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0029",
      "text": "When (if) you match the challenge of the Treasure Chamber, obtaining the Golden Ankh relic, you win.",
      "page": 6,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        350.2,
        436.31,
        415.8
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0030",
      "text": "Reading the cards",
      "page": 6,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        439.2,
        209.19,
        461.2
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0031",
      "text": "While both the rooms and the relic have a description that explains what the cards does, most of the card is used by the hieroglyphics that represent both the challenge and the relic ability.",
      "page": 6,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        470.1,
        452.21,
        559.5
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0032",
      "text": "They are easy to decipher, and the game is more fun when you use them. Here is how to read them:",
      "page": 7,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        32.0,
        449.24,
        73.8
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0033",
      "text": "Dice Values",
      "page": 7,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        95.0,
        116.31,
        113.0
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0034",
      "text": "means one dice with exactly that value.",
      "page": 7,
      "bbox": [
        64.2,
        121.9,
        452.87,
        165.3
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0035",
      "text": "means one dice with any value. If it appears multiple times, each of them can be any value.",
      "page": 7,
      "bbox": [
        64.2,
        178.1,
        445.8,
        221.7
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0036",
      "text": "mean a dice with a specific value. If it appears multiple times, all of them must have the same value.",
      "page": 7,
      "bbox": [
        64.2,
        234.5,
        430.18,
        301.7
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0037",
      "text": ": Re-roll: pick a dice and roll it again",
      "page": 7,
      "bbox": [
        85.8,
        349.7,
        370.7,
