    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0042",
      "text": "Power Relics, Small Backpack You can use the relics every turn without discarding, but can only carry 2 of them",
      "page": 8,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        69.9,
        447.58,
        138.6
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0043",
      "text": "Exploring the Great Pyramid This game plays a pyramid with 5 rows where the Treasure Chamber can be anywhere (except on the initial row).",
      "page": 8,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        159.8,
        444.65,
        252.2
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0044",
      "text": "Separate the Treasure Chamber and the Entrance, shuffle the remaining cards and separate 4 of them for the initial row, add the Entrance to them.",
      "page": 8,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        265.0,
        438.92,
        330.6
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c0045",
      "text": "Shuffle the Treasure Chamber into the deck. Use the deck to build the 4 levels of the pyramid, then make the initial row with the cards you separated initially.",
      "page": 8,
      "bbox": [
        28.2,
        343.4,
        452.89,
        409.0
      ],
      "mentioned_figures": [],
      "mentioned_tables": [],
      "section_title": "Page Content"
    },
    {
